mvp-blog-story-in--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-out--></li><li class="mvp-blog-story-wrap left relative infinite-post"><div class="mvp-blog-story-out relative"><div class="mvp-blog-story-img left relative"><img loading="lazy" width="400" height="240" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OC_Who-Owns-the-Most-Satellites_Shareable-400x240.jpg" class="mvp-reg-img lazy wp-post-image" alt="谁拥有最多卫星" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OC_Who-Owns-the-Most-Satellites_Shareable-400x240.jpg 400w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OC_Who-Owns-the-Most-Satellites_Shareable-1000x600.jpg 1000w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OC_Who-Owns-the-Most-Satellites_Shareable-590x354.jpg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /><img loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OC_Who-Owns-the-Most-Satellites_Shareable-80x80.jpg" class="mvp-mob-img lazy wp-post-image" alt="谁拥有最多卫星" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OC_Who-Owns-the-Most-Satellites_Shareable-80x80.jpg 80w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OC_Who-Owns-the-Most-Satellites_Shareable-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/OC_Who-Owns-the-Most-Satellites_Shareable-100x100.jpg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 80px) 100vw, 80px" /></div><!--mvp-blog-story-img--><div class="mvp-blog-story-in"><div class="mvp-blog-story-text left relative"><div class="mvp-cat-date-wrap left relative"><span class="mvp-cd-cat left relative">空间</span><span class="mvp-cd-date left relative">1 个月前</span></div><!--mvp-cat-date-wrap-->哪些公司拥有最多的卫星？</h2><p>尽管星链在行业中占据主导地位，但该公司在未来几年将面临激烈的竞争。 </p></div><!--mvp-blog-story-text--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-in--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-out--></li><li class="mvp-blog-story-wrap left relative infinite-post"><div class="mvp-blog-story-out relative"><div class="mvp-blog-story-img left relative"><img loading="lazy" width="400" height="240" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Google-Global-Market-Share_Shareable-400x240.jpg" class="mvp-reg-img lazy wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Google-Global-Market-Share_Shareable-400x240.jpg 400w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Google-Global-Market-Share_Shareable-1000x600.jpg 1000w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Google-Global-Market-Share_Shareable-590x354.jpg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /><img loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Google-Global-Market-Share_Shareable-80x80.jpg" class="mvp-mob-img lazy wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Google-Global-Market-Share_Shareable-80x80.jpg 80w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Google-Global-Market-Share_Shareable-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Google-Global-Market-Share_Shareable-100x100.jpg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 80px) 100vw, 80px" /></div><!--mvp-blog-story-img--><div class="mvp-blog-story-in"><div class="mvp-blog-story-text left relative"><div class="mvp-cat-date-wrap left relative"><span class="mvp-cd-cat left relative">技术</span><span class="mvp-cd-date left relative">2 个月前</span></div><!--mvp-cat-date-wrap-->可视化 Google 搜索引擎市场份额</h2><p>谷歌在搜索引擎市场的主导地位促使美国司法部就反竞争行为提起诉讼。 </p></div><!--mvp-blog-story-text--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-in--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-out--></li><li class="mvp-blog-story-wrap left relative infinite-post"><div class="mvp-blog-story-out relative"><div class="mvp-blog-story-img left relative"><img loading="lazy" width="400" height="240" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/202