元的资产。以下是该公司持有的主要股权。 </p></div><!--mvp-blog-story-text--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-in--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-out--></li><li class="mvp-blog-story-wrap left relative infinite-post"><div class="mvp-blog-story-out relative"><div class="mvp-blog-story-img left relative"><img loading="lazy" width="400" height="240" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Forecasts-for-Major-Asset-Classes_SHARE-400x240.jpg" class="mvp-reg-img lazy wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Forecasts-for-Major-Asset-Classes_SHARE-400x240.jpg 400w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Forecasts-for-Major-Asset-Classes_SHARE-1000x600.jpg 1000w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Forecasts-for-Major-Asset-Classes_SHARE-590x354.jpg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /><img loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Forecasts-for-Major-Asset-Classes_SHARE-80x80.jpg" class="mvp-mob-img lazy wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Forecasts-for-Major-Asset-Classes_SHARE-80x80.jpg 80w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Forecasts-for-Major-Asset-Classes_SHARE-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Forecasts-for-Major-Asset-Classes_SHARE-100x100.jpg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 80px) 100vw, 80px" /></div><!--mvp-blog-story-img--><div class="mvp-blog-story-in"><div class="mvp-blog-story-text left relative"><div class="mvp-cat-date-wrap left relative"><span class="mvp-cd-cat left relative">投资者教育</span><span class="mvp-cd-date left relative">5个月前</span></div><!--mvp-cat-date-wrap-->主要资产类别的十年年化预测</h2><p>该信息图使用 Vanguard 的数据可视化股票和固定收益的 10 年年化预测。 </p></div><!--mvp-blog-story-text--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-in--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-out--></li><li class="mvp-blog-story-wrap left relative infinite-post"><div class="mvp-blog-story-out relative"><div class="mvp-blog-story-img left relative"><img loading="lazy" width="400" height="240" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/AC_Spectrum-of-Market-Returns_Shareable-400x240.jpeg" class="mvp-reg-img lazy wp-post-image" alt="资产分配" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/AC_Spectrum-of-Market-Returns_Shareable-400x240.jpeg 400w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/AC_Spectrum-of-Market-Returns_Shareable-1000x600.jpeg 1000w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/AC_Spectrum-of-Market-Returns_Shareable-590x354.jpeg 590w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /><img loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/AC_Spectrum-of-Market-Returns_Shareable-80x80.jpeg" class="mvp-mob-img lazy wp-post-image" alt="资产分配" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/AC_Spectrum-of-Market-Returns_Shareable-80x80.jpeg 80w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/AC_Spectrum-of-Market-Returns_Shareable-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/AC_Spectrum-of-Market-Returns_Shareable-100x100.jpeg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 80px) 100vw, 80px" /></div><!--mvp-blog-story-img--><div class="mvp-blog-story-in"><div class="mvp-blog-story-text left relative"><div class="mvp-cat-date-wrap left relative"><span class="mvp-cd-cat left relative">投资者教育</span><span class="mvp-cd-date left relative">7个月前</span></div><!--mvp-cat-date-wrap-->可视化 90 年来的股票和债券投资组合表现</h2><p>过去 90 年来，股票和债券不同投资组合配置的投资回报如何？ </p></div><!--mvp-blog-story-text--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-in--></div><!--mvp-blog-story-out--></li><li class="mvp-blog-story-wrap left relative infinite-post"><div class="mvp-blog-story-out relative"><div class="mvp-blog-story-img left relative"><img loading="laz